playstore_details.title: Vimeo Create - Video Maker & Editor
playstore_details.description:
Create stunning videos in minutes - even if you’ve never made a video before.
Vimeo Create - Video Maker & Editor is an easy way to make high-impact videos that help you stand out on social media and boost your brand. Our smart video maker and hundreds of custom-designed video templates radically simplify video creation for anyone in any moment. Create is the new power tool from Vimeo, the world's leading professional video platform and community of 90 millionusers worldwide.
